title: The Ernies - Meson Ray
description:
The Ernies - Meson Ray

Heavy-hitting, hard-rocking, hip-hop influenced hard rock that you can dance too? You don't hear about this every day, but Richmond, Virginia's The Ernies seem to have captured the attitude all-too-well. On their major-label debut, they craft heavy rock riffs with scratching and sampling to shake things up, while trying to leave all in suspense.
